#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rank.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.rank"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:1 of
msgid "Compute numerical data ranks (1 through n) along axis."
msgstr "沿轴计算数值数据的排名（从1到n）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:3 of
msgid ""
"By default, equal values are assigned a rank that is the average of the "
"ranks of those values."
msgstr "默认情况下，相等的值会被分配一个等于这些值排名平均数的排名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:6 of
msgid "Index to direct ranking."
msgstr "用于指定排序方向的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:8 of
msgid ""
"How to rank the group of records that have the same value (i.e. ties):  *"
" average: average rank of the group * min: lowest rank in the group * "
"max: highest rank in the group * first: ranks assigned in order they "
"appear in the array * dense: like 'min', but rank always increases by 1 "
"between groups."
msgstr ""
"如何对具有相同值（即并列）的记录组进行排名：  * average: 组内排名的平均值"
" * min: 组内的最低排名 * max: 组内的最高排名 * first: 按照它们在数组中"
"出现的顺序分配排名 * dense: 类似 'min'，但组间排名始终增加1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:8 of
msgid "How to rank the group of records that have the same value (i.e. ties):"
msgstr "如何对具有相同值（即并列）的记录组进行排名："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:10 of
msgid "average: average rank of the group"
msgstr "average: 组内排名的平均值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:11 of
msgid "min: lowest rank in the group"
msgstr "min: 组内的最低排名"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:12 of
msgid "max: highest rank in the group"
msgstr "max: 组内的最高排名"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:13 of
msgid "first: ranks assigned in order they appear in the array"
msgstr "first: 按照它们在数组中出现的顺序分配排名"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:14 of
msgid "dense: like 'min', but rank always increases by 1 between groups."
msgstr "dense: 类似 'min'，但组间排名始终增加1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:16 of
msgid "For DataFrame objects, rank only numeric columns if set to True."
msgstr "对于 DataFrame 对象，如果设置为 True，则仅对数值列进行排名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:18 of
msgid ""
"How to rank NaN values:  * keep: assign NaN rank to NaN values * top: "
"assign lowest rank to NaN values * bottom: assign highest rank to NaN "
"values"
msgstr ""
"如何对 NaN 值进行排名：  * keep: 将 NaN 排名分配给 NaN 值 * top: 将最低"
"排名分配给 NaN 值 * bottom: 将最高排名分配给 NaN 值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:18 of
msgid "How to rank NaN values:"
msgstr "如何对 NaN 值进行排名："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:20 of
msgid "keep: assign NaN rank to NaN values"
msgstr "keep: 将 NaN 排名分配给 NaN 值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:21 of
msgid "top: assign lowest rank to NaN values"
msgstr "top: 将最低排名分配给 NaN 值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:22 of
msgid "bottom: assign highest rank to NaN values"
msgstr "bottom: 将最高排名分配给 NaN 值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:24 of
msgid "Whether or not the elements should be ranked in ascending order."
msgstr "是否应按升序对元素进行排名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:26 of
msgid "Whether or not to display the returned rankings in percentile form."
msgstr "是否以百分位数形式显示返回的排名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:30 of
msgid "Return a Series or DataFrame with data ranks as values."
msgstr "返回一个以数据排名为值的 Series 或 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`core.groupby.GroupBy.rank`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:36 of
msgid "Rank of values within each group."
msgstr "每个组内值的排名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:39 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:53 of
msgid ""
"The following example shows how the method behaves with the above "
"parameters:"
msgstr "以下示例展示了该方法在使用上述参数时的行为："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:56 of
msgid ""
"default_rank: this is the default behaviour obtained without using any "
"parameter."
msgstr "default_rank: 这是在不使用任何参数时获得的默认行为。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:58 of
msgid ""
"max_rank: setting ``method = 'max'`` the records that have the same "
"values are ranked using the highest rank (e.g.: since 'cat' and 'dog' are"
" both in the 2nd and 3rd position, rank 3 is assigned.)"
msgstr ""
"max_rank: 设置 ``method = 'max'`` 时，具有相同值的记录将使用最高排名进行"
"排名（例如：由于 'cat' 和 'dog' 都在第2和第3位，因此分配排名3。）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:61 of
msgid ""
"NA_bottom: choosing ``na_option = 'bottom'``, if there are records with "
"NaN values they are placed at the bottom of the ranking."
msgstr ""
"NA_bottom: 选择 ``na_option = 'bottom'``，如果有包含 NaN 值的记录，它们会"
"被放置在排名的底部。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.rank.rank:63 of
msgid ""
"pct_rank: when setting ``pct = True``, the ranking is expressed as "
"percentile rank."
msgstr "pct_rank: 当设置 ``pct = True`` 时，排名会以百分位数排名表示。"

